  • public class DPBackwardRecursionPeriod
extends AbstractPeriodWrapper
    This is wrapper class for an AbstractLotSizingPeriod object, which has members to solve the problem as a dynamic program

      • solve

        public void solve()
           throws SolvingInitialisiationException,
                  WrongOptimisationOrderException
        Goes through all the possible decisions and writes the partial optimal one into optimalDecision and the partial optimal value to partialOptimalValue
        Throws:
        SolvingInitialisiationException - if the vector possibleDecisions is empty
        WrongOptimisationOrderException - if the solving is not in backwards recursion order
